intent.user_query: What is the monthly trend of new customer registrations in 2023, showing the count of new customers registered each month?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM RegistrationDate) AS RegistrationMonth, COUNT(CustomerID) AS NewCustomerCount FROM fitness_db.Customers WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM RegistrationDate) = 2023 GROUP BY RegistrationMonth ORDER BY RegistrationMonth;

arguments.sql: SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM RegistrationDate) AS RegistrationMonth, COUNT(CustomerID) AS NewCustomerCount FROM fitness_db.Customers WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM RegistrationDate) = 2023 GROUP BY RegistrationMonth ORDER BY RegistrationMonth;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
